lead_paragraph: Brekkott Chapman had 15 points and No. 22 Utah blitzed Arizona State 81-46 on Thursday night, scoring the first 15 points of the game and opening a 30-2 lead on the way to its fifth straight victory.

headline.print_headline: No. 22 Utah Builds 30-2 Lead in 81-46 Rout of Arizona State
